title: Kids.Baking.Championship.S01E01.PDTV.x264-JIVE.mp4
description:
Hosts and Judges Duff Goldman and Valerie Bertinelli are putting eight child prodigy bakers, ranging in age from 10 to 13, through challenges to find the most impressive and talented one of the baking bunch. Each young contestant will be tested on their baking skills and originality as they create delectable desserts, including mouth-watering cakes, cookies and pastries.

The pint-sized winner of Kids Baking Championship will take home the grand prize package consisting of a set of Food Network bakeware, a profile in Food Network Magazine, an original cake featured at Charm City Cakes and $10,000.




Kids Baking Championship - Season 1, Episode 1



Bake Sale

For this kick off to the Kids Baking Championship, the kid bakers are hard at work to serve up two delicious signature items for a bake sale. Midway through the challenge, Duff and Valerie reveal that the kids must also make a third item using a classic childhood flavor combination.


Original Air Date: 02-Feb-2015
